{"tid":409868,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英法例：無執業證書不可自稱當地律師","createTime":"2017-09-22T12:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T07:34:52.000Z","uid":5195,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c366f4e58eead552284663a693b35d50a713964a","tid":409868,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:09:58.000Z","msg":"在立法會競選時自稱是「英國及威爾斯執業律師」的立法會議員何君堯，被質疑專業資格。何君堯今日回應《立場》查詢時稱，自己的確有在英國及新加坡註冊，「只是沒有執業」。立法會議員謝偉俊認為，如未有執業，應講清楚沒有執業證書，較為穩當。根據英國Solicitors Act 1974（執業律師條例1974），任何人以事務律師（Solicitor）行事，須符合三個資格，當中包括了合資格的「執業證書（practising certificate）」<br />\n<br />\n立場新聞》記者翻查英國法例《Solicitors Act》，條文列明以事務律師（Solicitor）行事（act）須符合三個資格，包括登記為事務律師、在事務律師名冊上，並有合資格的「執業證書（practising certificate）」。執業律師條例同時規定，任何不符資格的人士，宣稱自己作為（act as ）事務律師，也屬違法。"},{"pid":"21104d2be4a67fb418ecd7202d581ef615bcc4e3","tid":409868,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ed6497a73ee994e60d89c9e65e0b206d8cade8","tid":409868,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:12:53.000Z","msg":"隊友都要插佢一刀"},{"pid":"8f47547152bfd7c8e20f762def88bb1390401aa9","tid":409868,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:20:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/1974/47/section/21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legislation.gov.uk%2Fukpga%2F1974%2F47%2Fsection%2F21&d=zO%2FjE4h7bd6oxmBH%2BWRXN1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=6d746a00\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/1974/47/section/21</a><br />\n<br />\nSolicitors Act 1974<br />\n<br />\nSection 21 Unqualified person not to pretend to be a solicitor.<br />\n<br />\nAny unqualified person who wilfully pretends to be, or takes or uses any name, title, addition or description implying that he is, qualified or recognised by law as qualified to act as a solicitor shall be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding the fourth level on the standard scale"},{"pid":"442dde8b137f58b33cd331cfb424395b6530dc6f","tid":409868,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/1974/47/section/21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legislation.gov.uk%2Fukpga%2F1974%2F47%2Fsection%2F21&d=zO%2FjE4h7bd6oxmBH%2BWRXN1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=6d746a00\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/1974/47/section/21</a><br />\n<br />\nSolicitors Act 1974<br />\n<br />\nSection 21 Unqualified person not to pretend to be a solicitor.<br />\n<br />\nAny unqualified person who wilfully pretends to be, or takes or uses any name, title, addition or description implying that he is, qualified or recognised by law as qualified to act as a solicitor shall be guilty of an offence and liable on summary conviction to a fine not exceeding the fourth level on the standard scale</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0b9a2893c6f4bf3aa6298bcfcda3ae981f629c","tid":409868,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:22:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>立場新聞》記者翻查英國法例《Solicitors Act》，條文列明以事務律師（Solicitor）行事（act）須符合三個資格，包括登記為事務律師、在事務律師名冊上，並有合資格的「執業證書（practising certificate）」。執業律師條例同時規定，任何不符資格的人士，宣稱自己作為（act as ）事務律師，也屬違法。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n立場新聞睇section 20<br />\n<br />\n其實應該係section 21<br />\n<br />\n何生無practise UK laws既行為, 20 act as 好難中"},{"pid":"e51410ce5f5354c0a4c6e43a71e430c2592afa16","tid":409868,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:23:21.000Z","msg":"唯一出路，認低威，走港獨路線"},{"pid":"d49f3c43e00408d566b39fcf43baec0f4a0b6eb3","tid":409868,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi